{"tid":1565330,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"嘈黎無意思 我地915用人數證明唱歌係唔會搞散場運動","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:57:28.000Z","uid":1206,"like":130,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0cbaa3c0a6bdd87a5e0674b8668caae92cd557","tid":1565330,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:03:26.000Z","msg":"音樂一直都係最和平而強大既武器<br />\nWinter on Fire大家都有睇 佢地係唱住國歌抗爭<br />\n依個大家咁Lost 咁灰既時刻 的確需要一樣野去回血<br />\n知唔知一首歌既力量 其實可以好大<br />\n你睇下對家 係我地圍狗屋既時候 會唔會出黎搞事?<br />\n但依家唱左幾日 已經連吹兩次雞去唱鬼國歌<br />\n<br />\n但係連登依家成日有Post話有5年前柒味 又話會散又剩<br />\n我地嘈黎無意思<br />\n好簡單 915 大家行出黎 證明weekdays我地唱唔唱歌 做正經事既時候我地都會出黎<br />\n手足<br />\n915<br />\n3點鐘<br />\n東角見<br />\n<br />\n我諗個post好快有文宣洗板 我就唔Post圖了"},{"pid":"38fb4931a8cd8c65d121d74e026324b6c890f99a","tid":1565330,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"自推20次<br />\n915 東角見"},{"pid":"4c3e9bc7ae9f9b2a9bd23a08251f9a6345d55770","tid":1565330,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:03:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e833ca8773e94a542d58caeedfaec95fd4cf0027","tid":1565330,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:05:26.000Z