476795704610/posts/2253137151438559?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2253137151438559%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=cbdb2d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2253137151438559?sfns=mo</a><br />\n韓國人寫歌又拍片<br />\n歌：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GRqSSRBuVfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGRqSSRBuVfQ&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=6bcc09bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GRqSSRBuVfQ</a><br />\n片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kor6mu01lGY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKor6mu01lGY&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=ae912a27\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kor6mu01lGY</a><br />\n圖：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B2JgR5dBlx8/?igshid=1jyzbuqriofhy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2JgR5dBlx8%2F%3Figshid%3D1jyzbuqriofhy&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=6c678077\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2JgR5dBlx8%2F%3Figshid%3D1jyzbuqriofhy&h=8b995ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B2JgR5dBlx8/?igshid=1jyzbuqriofhy</a><br />\n波蘭人又拍片<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y3iFiSiJYX4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy3iFiSiJYX4&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=e2961c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y3iFiSiJYX4</a><br />\n德國人直頭比我地嘅手足做難民<br />\n仲有好多其他不能盡數<br />\n唔該見到就留返個言多謝返佢地 長期作戰 聚人心唔係一下就夠<br />\n韓文：지지해주셔서 감사합니다. 5대요구, 하나도 빠져선 안된다.<br />\n1. 송환법 완전히 철폐<br />\n2. 폭동 규정 철회<br />\n3. 체포된 시위자 공소철회 및 무죄석방<br />\n4. 공권력 남용 강경 진압에 나선 경찰 문책<br />\n5. 행정명령으로 국회를 해산시켜 즉각 행정장관과 입법회 보통 선거 도입<br />\n德文: Herzlichen Dank f&uuml;r all Ihre Unterst&uuml;tzung. F&uuml;nf Hauptforderungen, niemand weniger! <br />\n1. Allgemeines Wahlrecht f&uuml;r den Regierungschef und auch Legislativrat. <br />\n2. Die Freilassung von festgenommenen Demonstranten. <br />\n3. Die Einrichtung eines unabh&auml;ngigen Untersuchungsausschusses. <br />\n4. Die R&uuml;cknahme der Deklarierung der Proteste als Aufruhr. <br />\n5. Die komplette R&uuml;cknahme des Auslieferungsgesetzes.<br />\n<br />\n中英：&ldquo;Five Core Demands, All or None.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\nFormally Withdrawal (without any ambiguity) of the Extradition Bill<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\nWithdrawal of the characterization of the all related conflicts as &ldquo;riot&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\nDismiss all charges made against demonstrators who protested against the Bill;<br />\nGuarantee no further charges will be made.<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\nAccountability for Police Abuse of Authority and Excessive Force<br />\n(Set up an independent commission of inquiry to conduct impartial investigation).<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\nDissolve the Legislative Council with an executive order;<br />\nImmediately implement Genuine Universal Suffrage <br />\n(direct election both the Chief Executive and the Legislative Council)."},{"pid":"ea04fb4ce4525f5ac82d02afb0fab5cf55f8c446","tid":1565330,"uid":25721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:16:25.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"3dd04083e417fdef33b686c67959471db27fd710","tid":1565330,"uid":211914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4771e18622377e2addca62a26bc0b5f52cfcf218","tid":1565330,"uid":247998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"915一定要夠多人呀!"},{"pid":"b8b6b25d46ac9941facff2b1c77909e3227a48fc","tid":1565330,"uid":159417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b419d249338b9cb7a01ee9d043a0b1390a1fc837","tid":1565330,"uid":1072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime